<html>
<body>

<h2>The multiple Attributes</h2>
<p>The multiple attribute soecifies that user is allowed to enter more than one value in the input element</p>

<form action="/action_page.php">
 Select images:<input type="file" name="img" multiple>
 <input type="submit">
</form>

</body>
</html>

